item.title: Panoramas from Delhi, India
item.author: jakob.kuelzer@gmail.com (Jakob Külzer)
item.description: I spent some time in India and at a few spots I took enough pictures to create panoramas. Make sure you click the links to the full version and zoom to the original size of the image. They’re huge and you can scroll around for a bit and discover nice details. Full version: India Gate Panorama! Full version: Delhi Rooftop Panorama!
